  "response": "While I can't provide real-time or updated information on specific institutes, several well-known training centers in Bhubaneswar have traditionally offered C programming courses. You might want to consider the following types of institutions:\n\n1. **Engineering Colleges and Universities**: Many engineering colleges offer C programming as part of their curriculum and may also provide additional training programs.\n\n2. **Computer Training Institutes**: Look for specialized IT training centers, as they often have certified trainers and structured courses for beginners and advanced learners alike.\n\n3. **Online Platforms**: If physical locations are not a requirement, online platforms like Coursera, Udacity, or edX offer excellent courses in C programming from reputable universities.\n\n4. **Local Recommendations**: It's always a good idea to check local reviews or ask for recommendations from friends or professionals in the field.\n\nBefore choosing an institute, consider factors like course content, faculty experience, student reviews, placement assistance, and the overall reputation of the institute. If possible, visit the institutes to get a feel for their environment and facilities.",
